survey_response.review_text: I was in search of a Prosthodontist since last 6 months for getting veneers done on the front tooth.  Since it was a kind of smile correction, I was not ready to settle for a doctor until I found it convincing myself which was of utmost importance. Though I visited multiple dental clinics none of them were satisfactory. I was referred to Dr. Shambhu by a friend. He is commendable at his work moreover he had a convincing approach about the procedure. He understood my requirement and suggested the treatment. The whole procedure went smoothly without any fear, pain or discomfort. I am glad I made the right choice of the doctor and would highly recommend. Thank You Sir!

review_reply.reply_text: Feels happy to serve you and your family. Thank You for trusting us and we promise to continue our service in future

survey_response.review_text: *** ** *** **** ****** ** *** *** ***** ** ********* *** ****** ********* Both Dr Shambu and Dr Aarti are highly qualified and are extremely skilled and talented in all kinds of dental treatments. I consulted them for multiple root canals, Extractions & Implants. They guided me with me all the options and have executed the treatment really well. Both doctors have demonstrated amazing professionalism and are very approachable which i have not experienced anywhere else.  And they even have xray machines etc. which makes this a one stop clinic for all kinds of dental problems. I am delighted with the way I was treated through out the time. Now my whole family is getting treatment from them and all of us have the same experience.

survey_response.review_text:
My visit was in Dec-2018 for teeth reshaping and subsequently in Feb-2019 for Wisdom Tooth Extraction.

Both the doctors ... Dr. Shambhu and Dr. Aarti are excellent professionals and treat you with their excellent skills. 

Dr. Shambhu explained me about the procedure of veneer placement over my front two teeth in a very detailed manner.The results looked perfectly natural and I was more than satisfied with the outcome.

The experience was even better when I visited the clinic for Wisdom Tooth extraction. I had all my four Wisdom teeth removed at once and right from the moment of starting the surgery till subsequent follow ups , Dr. Aarti was always answering to all my queries. So I totally recommend these two doctors for any kind of dental issues one may be facing.

So , a big thank you to Dr. Shambhu and Dr. Aarti!!!
I had a very good experience ....Staff was friendly ...I would recommend the doctor to everyone 👌 👍

Dr.Shambhu is professional and really helpful in making the patient understand  the dental procedure which the patient has to undergo. He is very polite and caring. He will make sure that you are comfortable during the treatment and I would recommend Dr. Shambhu for all the patients without a second thought. Thank you Doctor!!

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you sir for your kind words of appreciation. Motivates us to serve you better.

survey_response.review_text: Brilliant Doctor couple, with very professionalism and warmth. Dr. Shambu and Dr. Aarathi are unique and i atleast have not come across docs of this stature.
